---
title: Premium Fillet Steak & Hasselback Potatoes with Argentinian Roast Eggplant & Parsley-Garlic Sauce
description: A juicy tender steak is one thing, but the right condiment takes it to the next level of deliciousness. We've added a bright parsley-sauce
and a side of Argentinian-style roasted eggplant to give the classic steak and three veg a flavourful and worldly upgrade.
